quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  17,53,Aur meray bandon say keh dijiye kay woh boht hi achi baat mun say nikala keren kiyon kay shetan aapas mein fasad dalwata hai. Be-shak shetan insan ka khulla dushman hai
  17,54,Tumhara rab tum say ba-nisbat tumharay boht ziyada jannay wala hai woh agar chahaye to tum per reham ker dey ya agar woh chahaye tumhen azab dey. Hum ney aap ko inn ka zaimay daar thehra ker nahi bheja
  17,55,Aasamno-o-zamin mein jo bhi hai aap ka rab sab ko bakhoobi janta hai. Hum ney baaz payghumbaron ko baaz per behtari aur bartari di hai aur dawood ko zaboor hum ney ata farmaee hai
  17,56,Keh dijiye kay Allah kay siwa jinhen tum mabood samajh rahey ho unhen pukaro lekin na to woh tum say kissi takleef ko door ker saktay hain aur na badal saktay hain
  17,57,Jinhen yeh log pukartay hain khud woh apney rab kay taqarrub ki justujoo mein rehtay hain kay inn mein say kaun ziyada nazdeek hojaye woh khud uss ki rehmat ki umeed rakhtay aur uss kay azab say khifzada rehtay hain (baat bhi yehi hai) kay teray rab ka azab darney ki cheez hi hai
  17,58,Jitni bhi bastiyan hain hum qayamat kay din say pehlay pehlay ya to unhen halak ker denay walay hain ya sakht tar azab denay walay hain. Yeh to kitab mein likha ja chuka hai
  17,59,Humen nishanaat (mojzaat) kay nazil kerney say rok sirf issi ki hai kay aglay log enhen jhutla chuken hain hum ney samoodiyon ko bator baseerat kay oontni di lekin unhon ney uss per zulm kiya hum to logon ko dhamkaney kay liye hi nishaniyan bhejtay hain
  17,60,Aur yaad kero jabkay hum ney aap say farma diya kay aap kay rab ney logon ko gher liya hai. Jo roya (any royat) hum ney aap ko dikhaee thi woh logon kay liye saaf aazmaeesh hi thi aur issi tarah woh darakht bhi jiss say quran mein izhar-e-nafrat kiya gaya hai. Hum unehn dara rahey hain lekin yeh unhen aur bari sirkashi mein barha raha hai